AI Document Intelligence Platform

An end-to-end AI-powered document processing platform built using FastAPI, Streamlit, Celery, Redis, SQL Server, Docker, and the MVVM architectural pattern.

The platform allows users to upload documents (PDF, Word, Images), automatically extracts text using OCR, performs NLP-based analysis, and provides search, analytics, and document insights through an interactive dashboard.

Features
    Document Upload
        Upload PDF, DOCX, PNG, JPG, and JPEG files
        File validation and metadata storage
        REST API powered by FastAPI
    OCR Processing
        Extract text from scanned documents
        Background processing using Celery workers
        Queue management using Redis
    NLP Processing
        Document summarization
        Keyword extraction
        Named Entity Recognition (NER)
        Document insights generation
    Search and Analytics
        Search extracted document content
        View processing statistics
        Track document processing status
        Monitor OCR and NLP job results
    Dashboard
        Interactive Streamlit interface
        Upload and manage documents
        View extracted content
        Analytics and reporting
    Containerization
        Dockerized services
        Multi-container deployment using Docker Compose


Tech Stack

    Backend

        FastAPI
        SQLAlchemy
        Pydantic

    Frontend

        Streamlit

    Background Processing

        Celery
